[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     The mock collects metrics by name so the demo can summarize
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     what would have been emitted.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
