[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         })
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # --- Lumpy: specialty respiratory item ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Long zero stretches, occasional batch use.
